{"tid":1834045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612被射傷右眼教師入稟指警方使用非法武力追討賠償","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:36:39.000Z","uid":125168,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd55bba53d143ad7eb1f9bfe94162877cbea3a88","tid":1834045,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"612被射傷右眼教師入稟指警方使用非法武力追討賠償<br />\n<br />\n去年612金鐘警民衝突中被射傷右眼的通識科教師楊子俊入稟法院，指警方使用非法武力，違反憲法、人權和《警察通例》，並就其傷勢追討賠償。根據入稟狀內容，警務處處長為答辯人，原告楊子俊起訴警務人員去年6月12日在金鐘紅棉路和夏愨道交界對他施加的非法武力，足以構成侵權和構成非法行為，要求法庭下令警務處處長作出人身傷亡的賠償，以及宣布警務處行為違反憲法、人權和《警察通例》。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-22 16:08:59"},{"pid":"a1a61496c9cfca88d4e0c9e8e4e63f7d776cc7d1","tid":1834045,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3415406f9cf5ece606213f8f62294ed1f72aec","tid":1834045,"uid":35661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2abeb2ccbfb1853ba02bce5ea03529c232eff7dd","tid":1834045,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"應該又原告變被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d397e5a1fa0fdb4ef1ccce03ee015123bddfd68","tid":1834045,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecb7b526393a5036ac4bf357eec812d259288c2","tid":1834045,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928e1f4ed3eb0d1ccf89bb712d3cfb8c19dbf0fb","tid":1834045,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"盲咗幾多錢都賠唔翻<img src=\